trans-unit.source: Interface that is used by the host infrastructure for property editing to handle sorting and filtering functionality.
trans-unit.target: Interfaz usada por la infraestructura del host para la edición de propiedades con el fin de controlar la funcionalidad de ordenación y filtrado.

trans-unit.source: It is used to determine whether a particular object should be filtered out.
trans-unit.target: Se usa para determinar si un objeto determinado se debe filtrar.

trans-unit.source: Used to set a new <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> on the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" />.
trans-unit.target: Se usa para establecer un nuevo objeto <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> en la interfaz <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" />.

trans-unit.source: Declaration of the event raised when a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> is changed through a call to <see cref="M:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget.ApplyFilter(System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter)" />.
trans-unit.target: Declaración del evento generado cuando se modifica una instancia de <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> mediante una llamada al método <see cref="M:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget.ApplyFilter(System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter)" />.

trans-unit.source: Read-only property that returns <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> is a match for the object.
trans-unit.target: Propiedad de solo lectura que devuelve <see langword="true" /> si la instancia de <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> es una coincidencia para el objeto.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the property filter matches the property filter target; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si el filtro de propiedad coincide con el destino de filtro de propiedad; en caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.
La instancia de <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilterPredicate" /> que se va a comparar.

trans-unit.source: Used to determine whether this <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> is a match for a particular <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilterPredicate" />.
trans-unit.target: Se usa para determinar si esta interfaz <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> es una coincidencia para una instancia de <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilterPredicate" /> determinada.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if it there is a match between a property filter target and a property filter predicate; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si un destino de filtro de propiedad y un predicado de filtro de propiedad coinciden; en caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.
